.github/copilot/
*.md
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!docs/**/*.md
# Project skills ship in-repo so Claude Code auto-discovers them when opened here.
# Ignore everything else under .claude/ (worktrees, local settings, caches).
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**
